d Handling of LP Gas</p><p>Energy Products (Safety and Efficiency) Act 2000</p><p>Energy Products (Safety and Efficiency) Regulations 2012</p></section></section><section id="_cd8f6467-baab-4284-86db-b7a60edd1ef1"><title id="_720939ee-938f-47e1-a811-05142a380da6">6. Electrical</title><section id="_9b363544-f909-441b-8cf8-c7791398a128"><title id="_4429ca47-03c0-49da-acd2-f891aa99f316">Administering Authority</title><p>Office of the Technical Regulator, Department for Energy and Mining</p></section><section id="_61ebbcd2-d7f7-4172-ae7d-7e2aa01ab27f"><title id="_764e730c-d04b-454c-bb0d-ec81dc53d2c6">Relevant Legislation</title><p>Electricity Act 1996</p><p>Electricity (General) Regulations 2012</p><p>Energy Products (Safety and Efficiency) Act 2000</p><p>Energy Products (Safety and Efficiency) Regulations 2012</p><p>AS/NZS 3000 Wiring Rules</p></section></section></page>